net.sf.jclec.mo

Interface IMOEvaluator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.sf.jclec.IConfigure, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DTLZ1Evaluator, DTLZ1ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ2Evaluator, DTLZ2ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ3Evaluator, DTLZ3ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ4Evaluator, DTLZ4ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ5Evaluator, DTLZ5ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ6Evaluator, DTLZ6ParallelEvaluator, DTLZ7Evaluator, DTLZ7ParallelEvaluator, MOEvaluator, MOKnapsackEvaluator, MOKnapsackParallelEvaluator, MOParallelEvaluator, MOTSPEvaluator, MOTSPParallelEvaluator

    public interface IMOEvaluator
extends net.sf.jclec.IConfigure
    This interface provides the required methods that any class that evaluates a multi-objective problem should implement.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis
